@node HIST "History of the Maniac Manipulator"

 V0.9 - V1.3 ... Sorry, I forgot what changed from the very
                 beginning. Maybe this text will become bigger
                 as days go by ;)

 V1.4 .......... added thinpaz.font to the archive which was
                 missing in V1.3
                 added Speedball II patch
                 changed the guide

 V2.0 .......... totally recoded
                 added commandline-arguments
                 added user-defined memory-allocation
                 changed from 32bit to 8bit POKEing
                 GUI removed
                 lot of work :(

 V2.1 .......... added Hillsea Lido patch
                 added Oldtimer AGA patch
                 added Lords of the Realm AGA patch
                 added Theme Park AGA patch
                 added Christoph Kolumbus patch
                 added Whale's Voyage II patch


